{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"393af318d4","title":"陈毅对中侨委革命造反总指挥部的谈话","origin":"《陈毅言论集》（北京：红代会北京第二外国语学院红卫兵批陈兵团翻印，1967.5.10","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb962120ff","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":7,"articleId":"393af318d4"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"22f5bd1aa6","name":"陈毅"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9fc4e4ed42","type":"title","text":"陈毅对中侨委革命造反总指挥部的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"d3af1cff7b","type":"authors","text":"陈毅","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"2996f3da05","type":"paragraph","text":"一、首都归侨“东方红公社”和中侨“革命造反公社”的大方向始终是正确的。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"43ef21da36","type":"appellation","text":"首都归桥东方红公社带头撤出中侨委，是革命左派的革命行动。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"742dfb246a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、首都归桥东方红撤离以后要很好地进行整风，打倒“私”字。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"f375e6eea4","type":"paragraph","text":"三、今后不许冲和砸，要暂停有关尖锐批判对方（中侨委联夺）的文章和广播，而以正面宣传为主，“总指挥部广播站应广播毛主席语录，林付主席语录及报纸上报道有关全国各地的夺权经验。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"},{"id":"4ea2206eda","type":"paragraph","text":"四、各地归侨组织的联络站要撤出中侨委。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4"}],"page":{"id":"caf2996adc","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"393af318d4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}